c: 43
v: 32
t: "Ngakube bona bayawuhlukanisa umusa weNkosi yakho, yithina esehlukanisayo phakathi kwabo ekuphileni kwabo empilweni yakulomhlaba futhi sabaphakamisa abanye babo ngaphezulu kwabanye ngamazinga ukuze abanye babo basebenzele abanye futhi umusa weNkosi yakho ungcono kunalokho abakuqoqela ndawonye"